      <div class="col about-col-1 text-center pt-3">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-jug-detergent fa-5x fa-fade pb-5"></i>
        <p>
        We use eco-friendly gentle detergents without harmful chemicals formulated to keep your clothes fresh and clean so that your skin can stay happy and healthy.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col about-col-2 text-center pt-3">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days fa-5x fa-fade pb-5"></i>
        <p>
        Choose the dates that work for you. Our LaundroMate employees work hard to ensure your laundry is collected and delivered back to you in your selected time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col about-col-3 text-center pt-3">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shirt fa-5x fa-fade pb-5"></i>
        <p class="">
